      <akn:section eId="sec_8_1903">
        <akn:num>8-1903</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Consequences of a dangerous or potentially dangerous dog determination.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_8-1903_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>If the Mayor determines that a dog is a potentially dangerous or dangerous dog, the owner shall comply with the requirements of §§ 8-1904 and 8-1905 and any other special security or care requirements the Mayor may establish.</akn:p></akn:content>
